#22500
The Foundation of Beginings~
   As you begin to get your wits about you it is immediately apparent that
locations have changed.  As you look around at your surroundings there are
vast amounts of cosmic debris and a very unique Aurora Borealis like stream
coming from all around.  The only seemingly viable pathway exists towards the
North where violent sparks of cosmic lightning convulse along this ever
color-changing path.  The exits to the South, East and West lead only to
destruction
~
