#22760
The Black Road of Shadow~
   You have stepped onto a strange, otherworldly, wide, pitch-black road made
from compressed shadows.  It appears as roughly hewn black bricks laid in a
consecutive grid.  To the north and the south is an ever expanding shadowy
void that has constantly appearing, violent looking spatial cracks.  To the
east you can make out the lush, vibrant, majestic trees of the Forest Arden.
The black road of shadow continues west.  As you turn to head back the shadows
wrap around you forcing you back from where you came.  
~
