#22779
The Black Road of Shadow~
   You have stepped onto a strange, otherworldly, wide, pitch-black road made
from compressed shadows.  It appears as roughly hewn black bricks laid in a
consecutive grid.  To the north and the south is an ever expanding shadowy
void that has constantly appearing, violent looking spatial cracks.  The black
road of shadow continues back to the east.  To the west looks to be a strange
sub-basement interior.  
~
