#22780
The End of the Black Road of Shadow~
   As you finally reach this point on your journey across the black road it
becomes quickly obvious that you have seemingly appeared into the back storage
room of some strange bar or inn.  A large oaken, reinforced door lies to the
west.  Gazing quickly to the south and north shows a vast infinite void of
unrelenting chaos, sending shivers to the depth of your soul.  
~
